                            <li>Attempting to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Service</li>
                            <li>Using the Service to store or transmit malware or viruses</li>
                            <li>Harassing, abusing, or harming other users</li>
                            <li>Misrepresenting your identity or affiliation</li>
                            <li>Interfering with the proper functioning of the Service</li>
                            <li>Reverse engineering or decompiling any part of the Service</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

